						               													<description>A Aventura de Caboclo Bernando (The Caboclo Bernardo Adventure) is based in a true history of an unsung hero who saves many sailor lives at Brazilian coast of Esp&amp;iacute;rito Santo at 1887 setember 7th.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game mixes strategy, cooperation and the thrill of fighting a perfect storm. The players represent the fishermen at beach who should keep the rope firmly to help Caboclo Bernardo (a Brazilian hero) to save the sailors of a sinking ship and bring them safely to shore. The mission is dangerous, the fishermen may even injure themselves while pulling the rope from side to side to control it over the strong winds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Also, an element of surprise can put everything away! Secretly, one of the players is an evil traitor who tries to sabotage the mission. He will try to cut the rope and pull it the wrong way, delaying the work of other participants until it is too late.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Portuguese edition:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Este jogo mistura estrat&amp;eacute;gia, coopera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do time e a emo&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de lutar contra uma tempestade. Os jogadores representam os pescadores que, da praia, devem manter a corda firme para que o Caboclo Bernardo chegue at&amp;eacute; o navio e traga os marinheiros em seguran&amp;ccedil;a at&amp;eacute; a margem. A miss&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; perigosa, os pescadores podem at&amp;eacute; se ferir enquanto puxam a corda de um lado para o outro para compensar os fortes ventos.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Al&amp;eacute;m disso, um elemento surpresa pode p&amp;ocirc;r tudo a perder! Secretamente, um dos jogadores representa um malvado traidor que tentar&amp;aacute; sabotar a miss&amp;atilde;o. Ele vai tentar cortar a corda e pux&amp;aacute;-la para o lado errado, atrasando o trabalho dos demais participantes at&amp;eacute; que seja tarde demais.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
